<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />没什么，<delay20 /><20_2 arg="4" />不用谢。<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />毕竟我平时<delay8 />
受了你不少关照啊！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay20 /><20_2 arg="3" />居然是风信子<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且还是黄色的风信子呀<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊？<20_2 arg="4" /><delay20 />黄色的风信子<delay8 />
有什么问题吗？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="3" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />黄色风信子的花语<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />记得是<delay frames="40" />“在你身边就是幸福”<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" />等、<20_2 arg="4" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等等，<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你说花语？<delay frames="40" />
我可<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不懂那些东西啊！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />没事！<anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="3" /><delay frames="40" /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />没事的，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />。<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我明白，<delay frames="40" /><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我都明白！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">你、<delay20 /><20_2 arg="4" /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你到底明白了什么啊？！<delay20 />
喂、<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" />，<delay20 /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有听到我说话吗？<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />快醒醒～！！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />难道<delay8 />送花之前<delay8 />
还得考虑那么多事情吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />早知道就选<tag a="135" b="3" arg="0xcd00" />这种东西<delay8 />
当礼物了<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<20_2 arg="3" /><delay20 />为什么会把菊花<delay8 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />当作礼物送人呢？<anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且巧的是，<delay8 />还是绿色的菊花……<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">因为<20_2 arg="4" />这朵花可是绿色的啊？！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />把这么少见的花当成礼物，<delay20 />
我还以为你会很高兴呢<anim id="Sighing" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">不对哦，<20_2 arg="3" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay20 />
送人礼物这件事情<delay20 />
也并不是越稀有就越好的。<anim id="QuestionMark" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />举个例子，<delay20 />看起来像是<tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />，<anim id="Nodding" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是吃进嘴里却是<tag a="135" b="3" arg="0xcd00" />的味道……<delay8 />
要是收到这种礼物，<anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />你会怎么想？<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然它的确是很少见，<delay20 />
但你不会开心的对不对？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">什么？！<20_2 arg="4" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那不是很有趣吗！！<anim id="TakenAback" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是能收到那种礼物，<delay20 />
我可太开心啦！<anim id="Sighing" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" />感觉好像<20_2 arg="3" /><delay20 />牛头不对马嘴的，<10_4 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />还是算了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
总之谢谢你<delay20 />送花给我<anim id="Greeting" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说起来，<delay20 />周围的人常说<delay8 />
我看起来很可怕，<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我到底<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />哪里可怕啊？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" />这是怎么了？<20_2 arg="3" /><delay frames="40" />
难不成，你其实很在意<delay8 />
别人说你很可怕吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我觉得无所谓吧？<delay20 />
虽然你的长相和说话方式都很可怕，<anim id="Serious" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />
但我们也能像这样<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />正常地来往呀。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 03 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="4" /><tag a="110" b="0" />虽然你嘴上说无所谓，<delay20 />
但原来内心觉得<delay8 />
我的长相和说话方式很可怕啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><20_3 arg="8" />喂，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="1" />，<20_2 arg="6" /><delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你觉得呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">长得很可怕！</message>
	<message label="103_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">说话方式很可怕！</message>
	<message label="103_c" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="player" targetSpec="" />一点都不可怕……</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />长得很可怕<20_2 arg="2" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算你这么说<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
我也不知道该如何是好啊。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />与其说是长得可怕，<20_2 arg="1" /><anim id="Worried" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="50" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不如说是表情可怕吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那你只要一直笑眯眯的就可以了。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">笑眯眯<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay8 /><20_2 arg="2" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是这样吗？<20_3 arg="8" /><delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你的表情<20_2 arg="3" />很僵硬。<anim id="ColdChill" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="4" /><anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唔<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="109" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Sighing" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />果然是吧……<20_2 arg="3" /><delay frames="50" />
<20_2 arg="5" /><anim id="Serious" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />你是不是应该注意一下，<20_2 arg="7" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说话的时候用词和态度稍微温和些？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="110" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><20_2 arg="4" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />温和？<anim id="Nodding" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我明白了。<delay frames="40" />
<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不对，<delay frames="40" /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我明白啦！<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><10_4 />
<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也不对。<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="8" /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好的，我明白了！<delay20 />
尊敬的<tag a="110" b="1" />！<delay20 /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="111" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">突然很有一种<20_2 arg="3" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />小跟班的感觉<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以你这个说话方式<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还是不要勉强自己改掉比较好吧？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="112" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有道理。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="113" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />噢！<20_2 arg="2" /><delay20 />不愧是<tag a="110" b="1" />！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />毕竟我和你交情这么好，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你还是有好好看清我的内在啊！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="114" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><20_2 arg="6" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你怎么用起敬语了？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />都说了，<delay20 />
我根本就没生气！<pageBreak /><anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真受不了——！<delay frames="40" />
为什么<delay8 />总是有人<delay8 />
觉得我在生气啊？<anim id="Sighing" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">抱歉，<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="3" /><delay8 />是我会错意了……<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可是，<delay20 />你这种粗暴的说话方式<delay8 />
难道就没有问题吗？<anim id="Worried" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">就算<20_2 arg="4" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />你这么说<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那<delay20 />我就来用用<delay8 />
你挂在嘴边的“<tag a="110" b="6" />”这个口头禅好了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这样的话，<delay20 />
应该会<delay8 />稍微有所改善吧。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你倒是把用词<20_2 arg="3" />多少改一改呀<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唉，<delay20 />这就是<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />的性格了，<delay8 />
大概也好吧<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
